description:
The Super Animal World expansion for Super Animal Royale arrives December 9, 2025. Explore a new persistent Social Hub, where you can relax, meet NPCs, embark on quests, and enjoy cozy activities like fishing, bug catching, and hamsterball racing, between brutal fights to the death.

Join your super friends in a living social world, where you can explore, unwind, and matchmake straight from the Social Hub into competitive modes, including Animal Royale, The Bwoking Dead (infection mode), and SAW vs Rebellion (control point mode). After each match, return to the Hub to continue the Circle of Super Life.

author: Xbox
description:
The Battle Evolves. 

Dynasties of the East, a bold new expansion for Age of Empires IV, introduces four variant civilizations, each with unique units, tech trees, and strategic flavor inspired by real-world Eastern dynasties. 

This expansion also introduces The Crucible, a new roguelite RTS experience built for replayability. Players face unpredictable enemy waves, randomized objectives, and unlockable upgrades. No two matches are the same, and each decision shapes the path forward. Whether you're defending your Wonder, unlocking powerful Perks or testing your endurance.  

Whether you're a seasoned tactician or returning to the battlefield to reclaim glory, Dynasties of the East delivers the next great evolution in the Age of Empires IV experience.

You’ve conquered history. Now conquer the unknown.

description:
Pigeon Simulator is coming to Xbox Series X|S and Xbox Game Pass this November!  https://www.microsoft.com/store/productid/9nrhqlzx3900 

Being a pigeon is more than just roaming the cities, eating trash and annoying people sitting in restaurants. It’s a responsibility, to maintain order, keep the streets clean (poop not-withstanding) and contain any anomalous entities that might be terrorising the city.

In Pigeon Simulator, you and up to 3 other feathered agents are tasked with shouldering this responsibility as member of the elite Paranormal Examination & Kontainment (P.E.K.) Unit.

Swoop into this SCP-inspired co-op adventure on November 11th!
